ces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f607be40c3a0079baa516f4c3f38dc9e36b6059f","tid":1510843,"uid":26056,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T19:57:10.000Z","msg":"冇遊行示威既日子我覺得冇問題喎 唔通真係要冇娛樂咩 難得空閒同朋友/另一半岀去玩下食下好西都唔係好過份啫 唔好將成個運動變苦行 開始怪責同路人唔夠自己上心啊 唔係個個都會話俾全世界聽佢有付岀架 得閒loop翻日本社運失敗原因啦<br />\n<br />\n但明知有大型活動 上一秒post完香港加油下一秒就吃喝玩樂既就另計 呢d仲仆街過平行時空班港豬"},{"pid":"f988dbc64c88b6fe92c9ff46b569e625e0463a92","tid":1510843,"uid":191627,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:02:05.000Z","msg":"好多呢d人啦～<br />\n一、冇家庭負擔，唔洗供樓，唔明白民間疾苦。<br />\n二、冇時事觸覺，覺得咩都唔關自己事，除左失戀。<br />\n三、冇乜點經歷過挫折，就算經歷過挫敗，都唔識用個死人豬腦思考人生既每一個經歷帶黎既得著。<br />\n。<br />\n亦因為種種因素導致佢地少用腦，耽於逸樂。缺乏危機感和政治敏感。<br />\n我地唔應該太過怪責佢地。<br />\n反正都攬炒。<br />\n學下佢地既港豬精神。<br />\n輕鬆下咁啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8c791dd36a50857c4faa2d34c5d0d760eaa3e2","tid":1510843,"uid":226955,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"7c75c5ce4a3012e2458b4feeae3e5c3979ac69da","tid":1510843,"uid":135398,"like":41,"dislike":5,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"707a1ddcc402ad4b88e56d15064a1ec4f24050b4","tid":1510843,"uid":260934,"like":60,"dislike":4,"score":56,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"抗爭未完我都唔會po玩樂野"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:37:44.000Z","msg":"正確態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:14:28.000Z","msg":"要緊記歷史教訓，日本社運衰落幾十年嘅原因係當年示威者過於強調「苦行」，對參與者事大業之要求太嚴苛，參與人數逐漸減少，運動無而為繼。當然太過輕鬆嘅態度亦唔係一件好事，過度追求和平、歡樂嘅氣氛之下嘅抗爭好容易變成嘉年華式嘅示威，不利於運動嘅發展，嘉年華式嘅示威會導致士氣消耗，最後運動往往不了了之，2014年雨傘運動就係前車之鑑。<br />\n<br />\n所以心想上嘅平衡對之後嘅發展係好重要。有時係可以玩可以笑，但唔好太過沉醉，笑完就要回歸正事。同時，亦唔好將自己成日綁喺一個緊張狀態，間唔中都應該放鬆自己比自己玩下笑下。咁樣對運動嘅長遠發展先係最重要。"},{"pid":"4415933b7f6f997fb4057650432bfb8378b360a5","tid":1510843,"uid":12940,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:25:30.000Z","msg":"我都好撚憎嗰啲仲喺到吃喝玩樂嘅freerider<br />\n但一張嘢食相嘅背後 其實可能係佢發完幾日夢之後<br />\n終於都可以食到餐好少少嘅飯 一張半張咪由佢囉<br />\n唔係個個發夢都會po story話比人知嘅<br />\n放鬆啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e703f546341750034f0f190fd760528324bb30","tid":1510843,"uid":177858,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:38:33.000Z","msg":"最撚黑人憎係po完吃喝玩樂無耐，<br />\nrepost返啲新聞加兩三句caption鬧下個D光環拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無人想睇你玩呀 <br />\n成個暑假香港人都開心唔落 <br />\n對唔對得住前線班中小學生呀</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfada1bfa72a7cc2e6a73fa478e33aa53591a72","tid":1510843,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70201b27a82ef14fb361d13b66584aba5c831afc","tid":1510843,"uid":135398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"問心啦你班仆街，你地除咗打卡仲為香港做過乜野？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淨係講上個禮拜六日，你班仆街仲有冇出過黎啊？</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ed1175a4ba7aef87f752cc0088e97db6a31fe9","tid":1510843,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eacc26cb53410e3d4fa0b5a405631910ecb112e","tid":1510843,"uid":82829,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T19:11:58.000Z","msg":"可是，後來，由於運動變成不是針對個別政策，而是轉向參與者追求突破自我，於是變成苦行式的，過度批判同行者的苦澀路線。作者解釋社運後來的發展：<br />\n<br />\n「自我反省由於帶着強烈倫理色彩，忠於這些原則的運動者，會去攻擊不如自己認真看待運動的戰友，或是在沒辦法堅持原則的時候感到挫折。運動者無法對戰友採取寬容的態度，導致內部衝突和暴力，太着重於抽象的理念，容易陷入自以為是的危險」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:46:03.000Z","msg":"好同意"},{"pid":"9c49bba740dbb409c8b127c20155c46d5ac26ac8","tid":1510843,"uid":161209,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:55:54.000Z","msg":"on9 飯都要食架下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a048af1dfc8b5a2391574347f45572e0c7e409","tid":1510843,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e88b5bde38a283f90a77d26cca9334bbf6de2e92","tid":1510843,"uid":207476,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"579cbe26c41660d182703904fa073d2d062c43e9","tid":1510843,"uid":82829,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T19:09:08.000Z","msg":"諗起連登有人話次次發完夢都會po吃喝玩樂嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T19:48:36.000Z","msg":"其實好多人身邊都有藍絲/警察親戚ig個啲<br />\n又廢事太明顯del佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扮不在場證據 po舊相姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T21:05:38.000Z","msg":"你都冇犯罪 你講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc780306f941dcc0593c61229536ff682a1d8180","tid":1510843,"uid":216008,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T21:31:07.000Z","msg":"始終需要生活<br />\n總之佢地仲肯用ig做新聞台 仲肯出去發夢<br />\n吃喝玩樂何足掛齒<br />\n律己以嚴 待人以寬"},{"pid":"a4c0d5efd34cffe95e93cee9f7f59018bb9f1954","tid":1510843,"uid":307195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0d8c791dd36a50857c4faa2d34c5d0d760eaa3e2","tid":1510843,"uid":226955,"like":24,"disl